text:
Me and my family loved Anna's bungalow. It is cozy, clean, efficient, warm (we were there during winter holidays) and charged with very good energy. 
My parents enjoyed the patio, the yard and the porch with a cup of coffee every morning. It was so nice to cook there, the kitchen is well equipped. I loved the tableware. 
The good vibe of this place was part of the great experience of our holiday.
We recommend this house and are looking forward to stay there again.
title: Remodeled Mid-Century Bungalow
